My original response to your response was that there doesn't have to be a meaning to everything, not that FCFS matters at all.  If a conversation does turn to mean something other than what it started to be then there will be a line drawn somewhere to indicate it.  As it stands, this is just s discussion right now.<br>
<br>
Yes you are right when you say that FCFS is about respect...an unpoliced FCFS is just that because it is left to the people participating as to who is right, who is wrong, and ultimately who has the right of way.<br>
