<br>
Or perhaps you would /ooc or /shout that you were gathering folks to do the CS dragon.  Then perhaps they would respond and say, hey we got a group here for it and we'd like to attmept it right now, <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> do you mind?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->  And then a dialogue would ensue.  I trust and have enough faith in SR to open a dialogue and figure things out that would lead to a viable solution to everyone.<br>
<br>
I doubt in your hypothetical situation that you would continue buffing and trying to get your folks there faster so you could pull Kelorek faster than SR and kill him in front of them without telling them your intentions, nor do I feel they would attempt to pull Kelorek in front of you without saying something in /ooc or /shout stating their intention.<br>
